posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Moving made easy at The Dove!', 'Don’t miss out on a fabulous one, two or three bedroom apartments at an incredible price!', 'You will love the open floor plans and the spacious kitchen which is perfect for entertaining.', 'All of our apartments feature dishwashers, air conditioning and a private balcony or patio.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Spacious & Open Kitchens', '- Entry Way Coat Closet', '- Adjoining Dining Room', 'And Living Room Area', '- Standard Electric Kitchen Appliances Included', '- Utilities Included : Heat, Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', '- Ample Counter Top & Cabinet Space', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Dove Tree participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Call today to learn more about our community:', 'show contact info', 'Dove Tree', '1105 Lions Park Drive', 'Elk River, MN, 55330', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'xHZi7VUET9']
